Somebody who need constant validation from you or compliments from you?

00:00:08.082 --> 00:00:09.941
Tell me I'm pretty, tell me I'm smart.

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.280
What were you doing last Friday?

00:00:11.281 --> 00:00:13.041
