No shame in it. We all have our attachment disorders.

00:00:25.122 --> 00:00:27.761
This is called ambivalent attachment disorder,

00:00:27.762 --> 00:00:29.001
and it is one of the disorders

00:00:29.002 --> 00:00:31.421
that Doctor Erica Commissar discusses in her book.

00:00:31.480 --> 00:00:33.800
