they're sometimes they're not sometimes,

00:00:52.521 --> 00:00:55.221
and the caregiving is inconsistent.

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:58.020
Just like all the other disorders we've already discussed.

00:00:58.440 --> 00:01:02.360
Ambivalent attachment disorder is that child's coping mechanism

00:01:02.361 --> 00:01:03.801
to deal with how they felt.

00:01:03.802 --> 00:01:07.021
They weren't given consistent care when they were infants.

00:01:07.080 --> 00:01:09.040
